아파트 근처에 공원이 있습니까 ?.

is there a history of brain aneurysms in your family ?.

is there a discount during off-hours ?.

is there that kind of ticket ?.
그런 종류의 표도 있어요 ?.

is there any reason to pay the earth for such an ugly car ?.
그런 이상한 차에 큰돈을 지불할 필요가 있어 ?.

is there any real information in the commercial , or is the advertiser simply showing an attractive image ?.

is there any particular song that reminds you of your mom ?.

is there any defensible argument for the bad thing he did ?.
그 애가 저지른 나쁜 일을 변호할만한 변론이 있나요 ?.

is there any corroborative evidence for this theory ?.
이 이론을 입증할 만한 무슨 증거가 있나요 ?.

is there an age limitation in applying for your company ?.
입사 지원하는 데 나이 제한이 있나요 ?.

is there (a) (steamer) service to the island ?.
그 섬으로 가는 배편이 있습니까 ?.

is there anywhere else nearby that might still be open ?.
이 근처에 문을 연 다른 식당이 있을까요 ?.

is that in celsius or fahrenheit ?.
그건 섭씨 온도예요 , 화씨 온도예요 ?.

is that the man you saw in the bar for a cert ?.

is that your car parked alongside mine ?.

is that why the new project was canceled so suddenly ?.
그게 새 사업안이 그렇게 갑자기 취소된 이유인가요 ?.

is cultural bias an important factor in the natural sciences ?.

is michael courting disaster by what he's wearing to court ?.
